    delegates to Ollama subagent. A deploy_config intent uses SSH. A research intent
    uses web fetch or subagent. Tool definitions stored in tool_registry.yaml.

    '
  acceptance_criteria:
  - Tool registry file exists at /opt/nexus/automation/tool_registry.yaml
  - Planning engine can list available tools and their capabilities
  - At least one intent executed end-to-end using a non-trivial tool
  - ECT costs deducted correctly per tool invocation
  - Tools requiring Md approval block and wait rather than executing
